A cross is mounted on the front wall.[p]
Long benches are lined up on both sides of a small walkway.[p]
It was as if time had stopped for this familiar style church.[p]
In front of the altar, a sly looking woman with cold eyes looks down at me with a eerie grin.[p]
As I walked up to her stepping one step at a time, she gazed at me without blinking. [p]
She looked as if she had predicted that I would arrive.[p]


